room_title: Escape room "Shenandoah Redemption" by The Lock Houston in Houston
review: This was our first escape room and it was a blast! We attempted to escape from prison and enjoyed great clues and an awesome setup. Glad I made this part of my birthday! We will be doing the other themes they offer great experience all around!

room_title: Escape room "Shenandoah Redemption" by The Lock Houston in Houston
review: We did the Shenandoah Redemption room. The clues were fun and challenging. The staff was very friendly. We will go back for another try at a different room for sure.

room_title: Escape room "Shenandoah Redemption" by The Lock Houston in Houston
review: We had an awesome time escaping the jail. This was a great event for the family and all had a great time, even the kids who ranged in ages from 7 to 11.
